<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4918727>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 161. A neighbor joining tree of specimens and species of Neotropical Lucilia using CO1 DNA barcode, made with K2P distance and generated in BOLD." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4918727/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4918532>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–6. 1–2. Left lateral view of gena=g and postgena=pg showing color of setae on gena. 1. L. cluvia, setae pale. 2. L. eximia, setae dark. Left lateral view of head showing condition of setae below and behind postocular row on occiput (white arrow). 3. L. albofusca female, setae pale and weak. 4. L. ochricornis female, setae stout and dark. Left lateral view of eye facet size, see white arrows 5. L. ochricornis male, anterior and posterior facets very small. 6. L. purpurascens male, anterior facets twice the diameter of posterior facets." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4918532/files/figure.png" .

